How Has the Law Evolved in the NIL Era of College Athletics?
How Has the Law Evolved in the NIL Era of College Athletics?

Monday September 15 - 12:00 PM to 01:00 PM

LOWELL E. BAIER HALL/IU MAURER SCHOOL OF LAW - Room Number: 124

Join IU Maurer's Labor & Employment Law Society in welcoming Mr. Stephen Harper '11, IU's Deputy Director of Athletics. He will be discussing how the law interprets the labor of college athletes and the evolution of labor laws in college athletics since NIL payouts have been legalized.
